CANADA: Bank of Canada to auction C$1.6 bln 21-day T-bills.Bank of Canada to auction C$1.6 bln 21-day T-bills.The Bank of Canada plans to auction C$1.6 billion of 21-day treasury bills on Wednesday August 21, the central bank said on Tuesday.  The auction will be held at 1100 EDT/1500 GMT with results announced at 1130 EDT/1530 GMT. The bills will be dated and delivered on August 22 and will mature on September 12, the Bank of Canada said.The tender is subject to standard auction terms.-- Reuters Toronto bureau (416) 941-8100